articles.title: Asian Para Games 2023 medals tally: Full list of winners from India | Mint - Mint
articles.description: Indians swept all the three medals in the men's F46 javelin throw event with Rinku (67.08m) and Ajeet Singh (63.52m) winning silver and bronze respectively.
